trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of the singular and plural forms of words.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção das formas singulares e plurais de palavras.

trans-unit.source: The singular version of the word added to the <see cref="T:System.Data.Entity.Design.PluralizationServices.ICustomPluralizationMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: A versão no singular da palavra adicionada ao objeto <see cref="T:System.Data.Entity.Design.PluralizationServices.ICustomPluralizationMapping" />.

trans-unit.source: The plural version of the word added to the <see cref="T:System.Data.Entity.Design.PluralizationServices.ICustomPluralizationMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: A versão no plural da palavra adicionada ao objeto <see cref="T:System.Data.Entity.Design.PluralizationServices.ICustomPluralizationMapping" />.

trans-unit.source: Adds singular and plural forms of a word to the <see cref="T:System.Data.Entity.Design.PluralizationServices.ICustomPluralizationMapping" /> object.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona as formas singular e plural de uma palavra ao objeto <see cref="T:System.Data.Entity.Design.PluralizationServices.ICustomPluralizationMapping" />.
